longBusinessSummary: SolarWindow Technologies, Inc. develops transparent electricity-generating coatings and methods. The company offers LiquidElectricity coatings for generating electricity by harvesting light energy from natural sun, artificial light, and low, shaded, or reflected light conditions, which is applied to rigid and flexible glass, and plastic surfaces to transform ordinary surfaces into organic photovoltaic devices. The company was incorporated in 1998 and is based in Scottsdale, Arizona.
